parameters:
\nc<>So, so, I heard that the hot springs here are amazing! What
do you think, senpai? Shall we go there next time?

\nc<>Ah...sorry, I'm not really into going outside the
prefecture.

\nc<>If something happens, I might have to go into action. It
might be difficult until this incident is over.

\nc<>Aren't you worrying too much? Candy-chan and Sherbet-chan
are also doing their best.
\nc<>Can you leave it to me for about a day?

\nc<>Mmm... Senpai, are you bored of going out with me? Come to
think of it, you've never invited me before...

\nc<>Well... I don't really know interesting places or anything
like that...

\nc<>I knew that Senpai was not familiar with that area from
before.

\nc<>I have some news for such a cowardly senpai. Let's meet in
the suburbs this weekend.
\nc<>I have something important to talk about.

\nc<>Yes. It's a very important talk, so please make sure to
come, okay? Also, I would be happy if you could invite me
next time.
\nc<>Hehe. I'm looking forward to it, both of you.
